<plot>A moral tale. Lieutenant Rizzo has arrived in North Africa at the start of the US Army's first battle against the German Africa Corps. As a combat camera man, he is ordered to get shots of the troops preparing for battle. Disobeying orders he hitches a ride to the front and learns about the harsh realities of war.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?187271</url></doc>
